creator: BabyBus
descriptionHtml:
Do you want to own a city of your own? Now, you can be the master of a city! Explore the city, run a shop, create exciting stories...Come and make your dreams come true!

EXPLORE THE CITY
This is a vibrant city with 6 buildings for you to explore! Do you like watching movies? You can spend your day at a luxury cinema, or enjoy shopping at a supermarket. There is endless fun for you to explore in every corner of the city!

RUN A SHOP
How can we make your city more prosperous? Open a clothing shop and design princess dresses for customers; run a pet beauty shop to give pets stylish looks; the dessert shop and coffee shop are also quite popular. What are you waiting for? Come and open more shops to make your city a cosmopolitan city!

CREATE STORIES
Are you bored of being alone? Don't worry! In your city, you can play with 18 characters and create fun stories. For example, go to the beach with friends; invite friends to try your homemade ice cream...Have sweet memories of your city!

More buildings are being updated. Come and unlock more cities and create your own world!

FEATURES:
- 18 character to play with you.
- 6 buildings for your to explore: Dessert shop, supermarket, cinema, coffee shop, pet beauty shop, and clothing store.
- Over 100 props, including lipsticks, eye shadows, costumes, and toasters, to help you create your city stories.
- Simulation of operation. Play the role of chef, pastry chef, designer, and more.
- Dozens of interesting tasks for you to complete: shopping, cooking, baking, designing clothes, hairdressing, makeup, and more.
- Buildings in the city are constantly being updated.

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

descriptionHtml:
Do you want to own a city that is all yours? Now, you have a chance to become the owner of a city! Everything is up to you here: you can explore the city, run a shop, or create wonderful stories... Let's fulfil your dream!

Let's explore 7 different, lively, and unique cities. Unlimited fun awaits you in every corner of those cities!

Cuisine City
Welcome to Cuisine City. Here, you can try out different delicacies from all over the world, such as cake, bread, juice, sushi, jelly, chocolate, anything you want! You can also make those delicacies with your own creativity and enjoy the fun!

Fantasy City
In this dream city, you can become a superhero and save the world. You can fight together with a robotic dinosaur, make interstellar delicacies, and explore unknown treasure!

Career City
Firefighter, veterinarian, astronaut, architect, photographer... When you grow up, what do you want to be? Come to Career City and experience different, interesting careers!

Monster City
Get a makeover for the monster. Play with your monster friends. Take good care of monster patients in the hospital. This is Monster City! Come and hang out with a variety of different monsters!

Family City
What is a day in kindergarten like? How can you take care of newborn babies? How should you clean up your room and keep your house clean? You can learn these skills in Family City.

More and more new cities are being added! Let's unlock more cities and create your own world!

Product Features:
-- Exploring 7 different, unique and lively cities.
-- More than 100 items to help you create your own story, such as lipstick, eyeshadow, costumes, and a bread maker.
-- Role-playing as a chef, a pastry chef, a designer and more.
-- More than 10 fun tasks await you, such as shopping, cooking, baking, designing costumes, hairdressing, and make-up design.
-- New cities are still being updated and added.

Want to own a city? Now you have a chance to become an owner of a city where everything is decided by you. Explore cities, run stores and create fun stories!

Explore 9 different and vibrant cities where you can have endless fun!

SAFETY CITY
Safety City is built! In this city you can take part in various interesting exploration activities, including simulated earthquake rescue, fire escape, and crossing the road safely. In the process you can learn a lot of safety knowledge and learn how to stay out of danger.

PRINCESS CITY
There are hundreds of makeup props, decorations and costumes for you to choose from in Princess City. You can put on a beautiful princess dress and makeup, go to all kinds of balls, and even take a ride on a float!

CUISINE CITY
Welcome to Cuisine City! It is a place where you can taste food from all over the world! Cakes, breads, fruit juice, sushi, jellies and chocolates are all available here! You can also make food with your own hands. Get creative and enjoy the fun of DIY!

CAREER CITY
What do you want to be when you grow up, a firefighter, a vet, an astronaut, an architect or a photographer? Come to Career City and experience a variety of careers!

MONSTER CITY
Give monsters beauty treatments, play with your monster friends, and take good care of monster patients in the hospital. Come and play with all kinds of new and strange little monsters in Monster City!

More cities will be added in the future. Unlock new cities and create your own world now!

FEATURES:
- Explore 9 different and vibrant cities.
- Over 100 types of items including lipsticks, eye shadows, costumes and toasters to help you create your city's story.
- Run different stores, take on the roles of chef, dessert chef, designer and more.
- Dozens of fun tasks for you to complete: shopping, cooking, baking, designing clothes, hairdressing, makeup and more.
- More new cities to come!

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

Want to own a city? Now you have a chance to become an owner of a city where everything is decided by you. Explore cities, run stores and create fun stories!

Explore 11 different and vibrant cities where you can have endless fun!

LOVELY CITY
There are lots of cute pets and friends living in Lovely City! Come here to feed, take care of, dress up and treat pets, or go camping, picnicking, and adventuring at sea with your friends. Have some fun and sweet time together!

ART CITY
If you like music, painting or crafting, then Art City is the right place for you! There are all kinds of musical instruments, paints and other items. You can play the piano, paint and color, make crafts and more! All you need here is your creativity!

SAFETY CITY
In this city you can take part in various interesting exploration activities, including simulated earthquake rescue, fire escape, and crossing the road safely. In the process you can learn a lot of safety knowledge and learn how to protect yourself and stay out of danger.

PRINCESS CITY
There are hundreds of makeup props, decorations and costumes for you to choose from in Princess City. You can put on a beautiful princess dress and makeup, go to all kinds of balls, and even take a ride on a float!

CUISINE CITY
Welcome to Cuisine City! It is a place where you can taste food from all over the world! Cakes, breads, fruit juice, sushi, and chocolates are all available here! You can also make food with your own hands. Get creative and enjoy the fun of DIY!

CAREER CITY
What do you want to be when you grow up, a chef, a firefighter, a vet, an astronaut, an architect, a photographer or other professions? Come to Career City where you can play as anyone you want to be and do anything you like!

More cities will be added in the future. Unlock new cities and create your own world now! Become a member now to enjoy membership benefits across platforms. Join us now!

FEATURES:
- Explore 11 different and vibrant cities.
- Over 300 types of items including lipsticks, eye shadows, musical instruments, paints, and more to help you create your city's story.
- Run different stores, take on the roles of chef, dessert chef, designer and more.
- Dozens of fun tasks for you to complete: shopping, cooking, baking, designing clothes, hairdressing, makeup and more.
- More new cities to come!

About BabyBus

We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.
